<section class="py-16">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 prose-custom">
    <p>
      At VisaJobs.xyz ("we," "our," or "us"), we are committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard information when you visit our website at <a href="https://visajobs.xyz">visajobs.xyz</a>.
    </p>

    <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
    <p>
      VisaJobs.xyz is a job aggregator and does not require user accounts or registration. We do <strong>not</strong> store personal data such as names, passwords, or resumes on our servers. The only personal information we may collect is:
    </p>
      <li><strong>Usage data</strong> — anonymized analytics data collected automatically through cookies and tracking technologies.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>2. Cookies & Tracking Technologies</h2>
    <p>We use the following third-party services that may place cookies on your device:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Google Analytics (GA4)</strong> — to understand how visitors interact with our website, including page views, session duration, and traffic sources. Google Analytics uses cookies to collect anonymized usage data. <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Google's Privacy Policy</a>.</li>
      <li><strong>Google AdSense</strong> — to display relevant advertisements on our site. AdSense may use cookies to personalize ads based on your browsing history. <a href="https://policies.google.com/technologies/ads" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Google Ads Privacy</a>.</li>

    </ul>
    <p>
      You can manage or disable cookies through your browser settings. Please note that disabling cookies may affect your browsing experience.
    </p>



    <h2>4. No User Accounts</h2>
    <p>
      VisaJobs.xyz does not offer user accounts, login functionality, or any mechanism that stores personal data on our servers. When you click "Apply" on a job listing, you are redirected to the employer's or job board's external website. We are not responsible for the privacy practices of these third-party sites.
    </p>

    <h2>5. External Links</h2>
    <p>
      Our website contains links to external websites (employer career pages, job boards, and resource sites). We are not responsible for the content or privacy practices of these third-party sites. We encourage you to review the privacy policies of any website you visit through our links.
    </p>

    <h2>6. Data Retention</h2>
    <p>
      Since we do not store personal data on our servers, data retention is governed by the respective policies of those third-party services.
    </p>

    <h2>7. Children's Privacy</h2>
    <p>
      VisaJobs.xyz is not directed at individuals under the age of 16. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children.
    </p>

    <h2>8. Your Rights</h2>
    <p>Depending on your location, you may have the following rights:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Request deletion of your analytics data from our third-party providers.</li>
      <li>Opt out of analytics tracking by using browser-level controls or privacy extensions.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>9. Changes to This Policy</h2>
    <p>
      We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page with an updated "Last updated" date. We encourage you to review this page periodically.
    </p>

